{
  "resourceType": "Questionnaire",
  "name": "Score2",
  "title": "SCORE2 — 10-year CVD risk (40-69 y)",
  "status": "active",
  "subjectType": "Patient",
  "description": "SCORE2 is the European 10-year fatal-and-non-fatal cardiovascular disease (CVD) risk model for apparently healthy adults aged 40-69 (no prior CVD, diabetes, CKD, familial hypercholesterolaemia, or pregnancy). Sex-stratified competing-risks Cox model with age interactions and four-region recalibration. Source: SCORE2 Working Group, Eur Heart J 2021;42(25):2439-2454.",
  "extension": [],
  "item": [
    {
